answers.question: Tell me about yourself. What interests you about this role?
answers.answer_text: So, hello, my name is Vishwas Kesheary and I am currently pursuing BTEC from the Anand Sagar University. I am interested in artificial intelligence and machine learning roles. I have built many projects like stock price prediction, driver drawsiness detection, in which I learned about feature engineering, model evaluation and data injection, hyper parameter tuning. I have also completed many certificates in machine learning domain, which was affiliated by IBM, given through Corsera. I think I am confident and quite quick problem solver. So, yeah, that's about me.
